title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1985-12-31
lineage: MAC > Tascam 112 > Edirol UA-5 > Audacity 24/48 wavs > R8 Brain 16/44 wavs > TLH > flac16; Recorded, transferred, edited, tracked and flac'd by Greg Holtz
description:
Set 1

Not Fade Away > Touch Of Grey, Tons Of Steel, C.C. Rider, Dupree's Diamond Blues, Cassidy, Brown Eyed Women, Let It Grow

Set 2

In The Midnight Hour > Sugaree, Man Smart (Woman Smarter), Ship of Fools > Playing In The Band > Terrapin Station > Drums > Space > Truckin' > Black Peter > Throwing Stones* > Not Fade Away* > Turn On Your Love Light*

Encore: 
Brokedown Palace

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums

Babatunde Olatunji - Percussion *

Opening Acts - Neville Brothers, Babatunde Olatunji

reviews.review_text: Best Aud source Pretty good recording in a crappy sounding building.
